{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2702490/extras/FullColor.png?t=1731958912\" />TETRACHROMA adds a new dimension to the block stacking action of classic tetromino stacking games: <i>the colors of the blocks matter!</i> Pieces appear in two or more colors, and to clear a line, every block in the line must match.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2702490/extras/GameplayPreview.gif?t=1731958912\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Transform the board with a new color changing mechanic inspired by the classic board game Reversi. Placing a piece adjacent to a line changes the color of the line to match. Plan ahead to maximize your score and clear 15+ lines with a single piece. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Modern stacking mechanics with wall kicks, lock delay, spins, perfect clears, and combos</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">40 hand designed puzzles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">5+ different gameplay modes playable in 400 line marathon and 100 line versions</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>STANDARD:</strong> balanced for general play</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>CONSOLE:</strong> classic retro console stacking mechanics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>BIG:</strong> double sized blocks for extra challenge</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>CELL:</strong> square board with modified piece set</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unlock 10+ block styles and 20+ color palettes by clearing modes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Speed settings for all skill levels: Peaceful, Easy, Normal, Hard, Master, and Death</p></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"MARATHON","path":"https://cdn.akamai